     H            Y.
      ***************************************************************
      *   ORDER RECEIPT ACCUMULATION DATA OUTPUT                    *
      *   DELIVERY INFORMATION / SUBJECT PARTS TAG WORK DATA OUTPUT *
      *   1997.02.17                                                *
      ***************************************************************
     F* ORDER RECEIPT ACCUMULATION DATA WORK FILE
     FDC#WP10 UF  E                    DISK
     F* ORDER NO CONTROL FILE
     FDC#WP20 UF  F       7            DISK                      A
     F* DELIVERY INFORMATION / SUBJECT PARTS TAG DATA WORK FILE
     FDC#WP11 O   E                    DISK                      A
     F* ORDER RECEIPT ACCUMULATION DATA FILE
     FDA#PP11 O   E                    DISK                      A
     I*================================================================
     IDC#WP20 AA  01
     I                                        1   20DCMM
     I                                        3   70DCNBR
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140WTIME
     I                                        1   20WJI
     I                                        3   40WFN
     I                                        7  100WYY
     I                                       11  120WMM
     I                                       13  140WDD
     I* EFU ISSUE DAY
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40B8FNYY
     I                                        5   60B8FNMM
     I                                        7   80B8FNDD
     I                                        1   80B8FYMD
     I* SHIPMENT ORDER DATE
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40B8TEYY
     I                                        5   60B8TEMM
     I                                        7   80B8TEDD
     I                                        1   80B8TYMD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80B8SAHZ
     I                                        1   40B8SAYY
     I                                        5   60B8SAMM
     I                                        7   80B8SADD
     I* P@YMD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   20P@MM
     I                                        3   40P@DD
     I                                        5   80P@YY
     I                                        1   8 P@YMDX
     I            DS
     I                                        1   40P@YY1
     I                                        5   60P@MM1
     I                                        7   80P@DD1
     I                                        1   80P@YMD1
     C*================================================================
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           P@US   10        USER PROFILE
     C                     PARM           P@YMD   8        IS THIS DELIVER
     C*================================================================
     C*================================================================
     C                     MOVE P@YMD     P@YMDX
     C                     Z-ADDP@YY      P@YY1
     C                     Z-ADDP@MM      P@MM1
     C                     Z-ADDP@DD      P@DD1
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C*--------------------
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ DC#WP101                 90
     C   90                LEAVE
     C*
     C                     EXSR #NBR
     C                     EXSR DA#PP
     C                     UPDATDC#WP101
     C                     ENDDO
     C*--------------------
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C*================================================================
     C* ORDER NO CONTROL FILE
     C*================================================================
     C           #NBR      BEGSR
     C           1         CHAINDC#WP20              90
      *
     C*===NO READ===*
     C           *IN90     IFEQ '1'
     C                     Z-ADDB8SAMM    DCMM
     C                     Z-ADD00001     DCNBR
     C                     EXCPT$ADD
     C                     ELSE
     C*===READ===*
     C           DCMM      IFNE B8SAMM
     C                     Z-ADDB8SAMM    DCMM
     C                     Z-ADD00001     DCNBR
     C                     EXCPT$UPD
     C                     ELSE
     C           DCNBR     ADD  1         DCNBR
     C                     EXCPT$UPD
     C                     END
     C                     END
      *
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C* ORDER RECEIPT ACCUMULATION DATA
     C*================================================================
     C           DA#PP     BEGSR
     C                     TIME           WTIME
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    B8SKBN           DELETE CD
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKYY           DELETE DATE YY
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKMM                       MM
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKDD                       DD
     C                     Z-ADDWYY       B8KOYY           UPDATE DATE YY
     C                     Z-ADDWMM       B8KOMM                       MM
     C                     Z-ADDWDD       B8KODD                       DD
     C                     Z-ADDWJI       B8KOJI           UPDATE TIME JI
     C                     Z-ADDWFN       B8KOFN                       FN
     C                     MOVELP@US      B8KONA           UPDATE WORKER
     C                     Z-ADDDCNBR     B8RENO           ORDER NO
     C                     Z-ADD*DATE     B8SAHZ           CREATE DATE
     C* DELIVERY INFORMATION / SUBJECT PARTS TAG WORK DATA
     C* SHIPMENT ORDER DATE
     C           B8TYMD    IFLE P@YMD1
     C                     WRITEDC#WP111
     C                     Z-ADDWYY       B8FNYY           EFU ISSUE DAY
     C                     Z-ADDWMM       B8FNMM                  MM
     C                     Z-ADDWDD       B8FNDD                  DD
     C                     ENDIF
     C**
     C                     WRITEDA#PP111
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     ODC#WP20 EADD             $ADD
     O                         DCMM       2
     O                         DCNBR      7
     O        E                $UPD
     O                         DCMM       2
     O                         DCNBR      7
